{"tid":2339395,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有經濟師料明年首季中國經濟按年增長逾20%","createTime":"2020-12-24T15:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T01:15:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c674ff467f26268b9728fdc600432eb5861304a1","tid":2339395,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566984-20201224.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566984-20201224.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt1%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=5f3b9f18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566984-20201224.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ed74e664\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566984-20201224.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n星展香港高級經濟師周洪禮預期，明年首季中國經濟按年增長逾20%，主要受今年首季低基數帶動。但由於基數效應逐步減退，第2至第4季增速會逐步回落至5%，全年增長約7-8%。<br />\n<br />\n他指，歐美疫情仍然嚴峻，對內地醫療用品需求大，如果疫情緩和，會進一步提振其他出口活動，帶動製造業延續今年下半年以來升勢，認為出口及工業產出會在明年頭兩季繼續成為主要增長引擎。<br />\n<br />\n提到中央今年因應疫情，罕有不提經濟增長目標。周洪禮指，不排除明年做法一樣，認為明確增長目標會限制政策發展及開放步伐。他相信，中央內部有指標，例如早前提出至2035年人均GDP翻倍，暗示未來15年中國經濟每年約有5%增長。<br />\n<br />\n周洪禮預期，財政同貨幣政策會逐步退場，財政赤字率會由今年3.6%，回落至3%至3.3%區間。人民銀行不會減息及降準。"},{"pid":"5bab00f93f2a53479ddc1e635724e84e9df52b43","tid":2339395,"uid":82669,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"全面脱貧，GDP翻倍，支支大赢家"},{"pid":"0c2c2be75400468fda9bbb6518d42f846d44b2fb","tid":2339395,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"陷球鏟 但益晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c77255aa922fbf1de597050dc0a8558e664e4d","tid":2339395,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":